eNCA's senior journalist Aviwe Mtila was in court and filed this report. Courtesy #DStv403 PRETORIA - Five alleged human traffickers who made their second appearance in the Pretoria magistrate's court are in the country illegally. That was the bone of contention for the alleged suspects who were arrested on New Year’s Eve. WATCH | Alleged human traffickers in court This follows the rescue of a 17-year-old girl as well as a 25-year-old. * eNCA's Aviwe Mtila reports.